v2ex.com/gravatar/7a4c4bbb84322b069036d29ad8e1658e?s=73&d=retro","created":1658391108,"last_modified":1666580786},"last_reply_by":"Yourshell","last_touched":1692671777,"title":"建议永久拉黑国外 vps 提供商：绿云（greencloudvps）","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/967270","created":1692668237,"deleted":0,"content":"没错，本人购买的是绿云 vps 特价版，表面看起来极具性价比，然而事实并非如此，3 天 2 头维护，维护期间 vps 不可\r\n\r\n用。试想一下，假如你运行某些重要服务，突然给你停机了，会给你带来多大损失。\r\n\r\n\r\n想退款，不好意思，特价版不能退款！\r\n\r\n\r\n我也买过其他 vps 提供商特价版,但是从未遇到绿云这样频繁出问题的情况。\r\n\r\n\r\n所以劝各位想买绿云服务器的朋友，避坑！\r\n\r\n\r\n自此之后，绝不再买任何绿云产品！","content_rendered":"<p>没错，本人购买的是绿云 vps 特价版，表面看起来极具性价比，然而事实并非如此，3 天 2 头维护，维护期间 vps 不可</p>\n<p>用。试想一下，假如你运行某些重要服务，突然给你停机了，会给你带来多大损失。</p>\n<p>想退款，不好意思，特价版不能退款！</p>\n<p>我也买过其他 vps 提供商特价版,但是从未遇到绿云这样频繁出问题的情况。</p>\n<p>所以劝各位想买绿云服务器的朋友，避坑！</p>\n<p>自此之后，绝不再买任何绿云产品！</p>\n","last_modified":1692668237,"replies":10,"id":967270},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":23161,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2675,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":363740,"username":"notproblem","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/notproblem","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f96e/7139/363740_mini.png?m=1662994375","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f96e/7139/363740_normal.png?m=1662994375","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f96e/7139/363740_large.png?m=1662994375","created":1542417102,"last_modified":1662994375},"last_reply_by":"PostMeridiem18","last_touched":1692671549,"title":"MacBook pro 如何保存外接显示器顺序的设置","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/967262","created":1692667526,"deleted":0,"content":"- 各位大佬，MacBook pro 外接显示器放在左边的，然后电脑默认设置鼠标要从右边划才能划到外接显示器。\r\n- 然后我在系统偏好设置中修改了显示器顺序，解决了问题。\r\n- 但是新的问题是，这个顺序设置好像不能保存。每次电脑关机后，或者有时锁屏后，又会恢复默认设置。然后又要重新设置一次显示器排列顺序，很麻烦。有知道怎么解决的吗？","content_rendered":"<ul>\n<li>各位大佬，MacBook pro 外接显示器放在左边的，然后电脑默认设置鼠标要从右边划才能划到外接显示器。</li>\n<li>然后我在系统偏好设置中修改了显示器顺序，解决了问题。</li>\n<li>但是新的问题是，这个顺序设置好像不能保存。每次电脑关机后，或者有时锁屏后，又会恢复默认设置。然后又要重新设置一次显示器排列顺序，很麻烦。有知道怎么解决的吗？</li>\n</ul>\n","last_modified":1692667795,"replies":9,"id":967262},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":209483,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3917,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":632971,"username":"PeaceJoy","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/PeaceJoy","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d4c9c98119b1bbb98069abb35e19d731?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d4c9c98119b1bbb98069abb35e19d731?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d4c9c98119b1bbb98069abb35e19d731?s=73&d=retro","created":1686131371,"last_modified":1686131371},"last_reply_by":"PeaceJoy","last_touched":1692671476,"title":"cloudflare 代理速度慢怎么优化","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/967283","created":1692670838,"deleted":0,"content":"在 cloudflare 上部署了一个 GPT 的代理，配置了自定义域名，但是从国内访问时，访问时间普遍在数秒以上，体验较差，想问问大家有没有办法优化？","content_rendered":"<p>在 cloudflare 上部署了一个 GPT 的代理，配置了自定义域名，但是从国内访问时，访问时间普遍在数秒以上，体验较差，想问问大家有没有办法优化？